Packages
org.pojava.datetime Utilities for parsing, representing, calculating, and converting dates and times.

org.pojava.lang Reusable elements that are not specific to a particular task.
org.pojava.testing Objects that aid in unit testing-- currently, by providing an InitialContext normally created by your application server for JNDI.

org.pojava.util Util contains pure utility code.
